{"tid":1746243,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷買藍店]唔好去Cinema  City 睇返校阿， 老細係奶共黃百鳴","createTime":"2019-11-22T15:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T07:08:10.000Z","uid":44057,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a236803286837fdbc30cd7561022637bde810def","tid":1746243,"uid":44057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"我知返校好少戲院上， 但真係唔好畀錢佢賺<br />\n其他會上嘅戲院我唔知個底係咩。但黃百鳴就好撚明顯啦<br />\n罷食咁叻嘅手足，請大家罷買CC 嘅戲飛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nd81Wth.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNd81Wth.png&h=6203cebf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRcaPOi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRcaPOi.png&h=3b1d8c36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ca28e795df565ba0834bad4dd6d2bdb853bcbdc","tid":1746243,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=a0870489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=ZU5rKlsKhNp37FgV%2FTwvgi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=d88e2ffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"http